00:11:34.930 --> 00:11:36.637
It's gonna go real fast.

00:11:36.637 --> 00:11:38.220
I was tutoring at
his learning center.

00:11:38.220 --> 00:11:39.300
One day a kid walked in.

00:11:39.300 --> 00:11:40.674
He couldn't multiply
polynomials.

00:11:40.674 --> 00:11:42.590
I love multiplying polynomials.

00:11:42.590 --> 00:11:43.290
He looked at me.

00:11:43.290 --> 00:11:44.623
He said, can you really help me?

00:11:44.623 --> 00:11:45.951
I'm like, dude, I got this.

00:11:45.951 --> 00:11:46.450
He comes.

00:11:46.450 --> 00:11:47.110
He sits down.

00:11:47.110 --> 00:11:47.980
I help him.

00:11:47.980 --> 00:11:49.830
The light turns on.

00:11:49.830 --> 00:11:53.050
He turns the book, and he sees
the answer, and he looks at me.

00:11:53.050 --> 00:11:55.030
He's like, oh, my gosh.

00:11:55.030 --> 00:11:56.110
It's that easy?

00:11:56.110 --> 00:11:57.250
I'm like, yes.

00:11:57.250 --> 00:11:58.230
