00:11:58.230 --> 00:12:00.980
I felt this thing that
I had never felt before,

00:12:00.980 --> 00:12:02.940
and I was like, oh, no, no, no.

00:12:02.940 --> 00:12:05.670
That's teaching thing.

00:12:05.670 --> 00:12:07.000
We're not doing that.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:10.230
So I told the lady at the front
desk who hired me-- I said,

00:12:10.230 --> 00:12:17.000
listen I'm not working here no
more because if you're telling

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:20.260
