thing feel that good,

00:12:20.260 --> 00:12:23.250
and I actually enjoy it, then I
gotta run from it because that

00:12:23.250 --> 00:12:24.080
doesn't make money.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:25.663
And I've already
been clear in my mind

00:12:25.663 --> 00:12:27.317
