00:35:30.850 --> 00:35:32.980
workshop; whether I'm
in Nashville, Tennessee;

00:35:32.980 --> 00:35:37.380
whether I'm in Seattle,
Washington-- what I experience,

00:35:37.380 --> 00:35:42.390
what I've observed, is
