So that's why I had to
keep praying for him

00:48:55.060 --> 00:48:58.830
and the rest of my children.

00:48:58.830 --> 00:49:02.760
And just-- life is life.

00:49:02.760 --> 00:49:08.890
With children, you have to
let them know, I love you.

00:49:08.890 --> 00:49:12.490
But one thing he knew,
when the teachers told me

00:49:12.490 --> 00:49:17.280
