I'm believing the teachers.

00:49:17.280 --> 00:49:19.830
I believe you, but I'm
believing the teachers.

00:49:19.830 --> 00:49:22.830
But he knew that I had
his back on things.

00:49:22.830 --> 00:49:25.590
But he knew that I
expected high of him.

