00:49:38.890 --> 00:49:40.530
You're not going to college?

00:49:40.530 --> 00:49:41.030
Nope.

00:49:41.030 --> 00:49:43.590
I've decided I'm not
going to college.

00:49:43.590 --> 00:49:45.040
I said, OK.

00:49:45.040 --> 00:49:49.560
Well just get ready because
you need to find a job.

00:49:49.560 --> 00:49:51.520
